# Git Learners Guestbook âœ¨

Welcome website team! This is a shared project for practicing Git and GitHub.  
Each learner should add their own entry below by following the instructions.

---

## How to Contribute:
1. Clone this repo to your machine.
2. Create a new branch with your name (e.g., `feature/your-name`).
3. Add your entry at the end of this file.
4. Commit your change with a meaningful message.
5. Push your branch to GitHub.
6. Open a Pull Request (PR) to the `main` branch.
7. Wait for review and merge.
